rtant}</style><div class=\"ugb-inner-block\"><div class=\"ugb-block-content\"><div class=\"ugb-button-container\"><a class=\"ugb-button1 ugb-button ugb-button--size-medium\" href=\"https://creditanalysis.valuatum.com/AspAndUserCreation.action?templateAspQueryKey=CreditAnalysis\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span class=\"ugb-button--inner\">Sign up</span></a></div><div class=\"ugb-button-container\"><a class=\"ugb-button2 ugb-button ugb-button--size-medium\" href=\"https://creditreports.dk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2020/08/valuation_report_demo.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span class=\"ugb-button--inner\">Sample report</span></a></div><div class=\"ugb-button-container\"><a class=\"ugb-button3 ugb-button ugb-button--size-medium\" href=\"https://platform.creditreports.dk/QuickLogin.action?key=3917&amp;x=qweasd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span class=\"ugb-button--inner\">Try the system</span></a></div></div></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:ugb/button -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Explore how this valuation tool works</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Video is provided by Valuatum, the software company behind this platform.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/RCqo-1ph-Gs\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></div>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:ugb/container -->",
  "localized_html": "<!-- wp:ugb/header {\"design\":\"plain\",\"shadow\":0,\"columnBackgroundColorOpacity\":0,\"columnBackgroundTintStrength\":1,\"titleTag\":\"h1\",\"titleFontFamily\":\"Poppins\",\"titleFontWeight\":\"500\",\"titleLetterSpacing\":0.5,\"titleFontSize\":56,\"showButton\":false,\"buttonSize\":\"small\",\"buttonBackgroundColor\":\"#313131\",\"buttonHoverEffect\":\"lift\",\"buttonBorderRadius\":100,\"button2Design\":\"ghost\",\"button2Size\":\"small\",\"button2BackgroundColor\":\"#313131\",\"button2HoverEffect\":\"lift\",\"button2BorderRadius\":100,\"button2HoverGhostToNormal\":false,\"uniqueClass\":\"ugb-81b09e3\",\"mobileBlockHeight\":50,\"mobileBlockHeightUnit\":\"vh\",\"blockWidth\":650,\"blockHorizontalAlign\":\"flex-start\",\"columnHeight\":650,\"columnContentVerticalAlign\":\"center\",\"showBlockBackground\":true,\"blockInnerWidth\":\"wide\",\"align\":\"full\",\"blockBackgroundBackgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"blockBackgroundBackgroundColor2\":\"#ffb20b\",\"blockBackgroundBackgroundMediaUrl\":\"/assets/wordpress-media/2020/08/block-background-background-media-url.jpg\",\"blockBackgroundBackgroundTintStrength\":9,\"blockBackgroundBackgroundGradientDirection\":40,\"contentAlign\":\"left\"} -->\n<div class=\"alignfull wp-block-ugb-header ugb-header ugb-81b09e3 ugb-header ugb-header--v3 ugb-header--design-plain ugb-main-block ugb-main-block--inner-wide ugb--has-block-background ugb--has-background-overlay\" id=\"\"><style>.ugb-81b09e3 .ugb-header__title{font-family:\"Poppins\",Sans-serif !important;font-size:56px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-align:left !important}.ugb-81b09e3 .ugb-inner-block{text-align:left}.ugb-81b09e3.ugb-header{justify-content:flex-start;background-color:#ffffff;background-image:url(/assets/wordpress-media/2020/08/block-background-background-media-url.jpg)}.ugb-81b09e3.ugb-header > .ugb-inner-block{width:650px !important;min-width:auto !important}.ugb-81b09e3.ugb-header:before{background-color:#ffffff;opacity:0.9}@media screen and (max-width:768px){.ugb-81b09e3.ugb-header{min-height:50vh !important}}</style><div class=\"ugb-inner-block\"><div class=\"ugb-block-content\"><div class=\"ugb-header__item\"><div class=\"ugb-content-wrapper\"><h1 class=\"ugb-header__title\">COMPANY VALUATION TOOL</h1><p class=\"ugb-header__subtitle\">Company valuation tool provides you a reliable estimate for the value of a company. As in our credit reports, the valuation report can be generated by either using automatically generated estimates or user-modified scenarios.</p></div></div></div></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:ugb/header -->\n\n<!-- wp:ugb/container {\"contentWidth\":65,\"contentMobileWidth\":100,\"contentHorizontalAlign\":\"center\",\"borderRadius\":0,\"shadow\":0,\"columnBackgroundColorOpacity\":1,\"uniqueClass\":\"ugb-6011e3b\",\"mobileMarginTop\":0,\"mobileMarginBottom\":0,\"mobilePaddingTop\":0,\"mobilePaddingRight\":0,\"mobilePaddingBottom\":0,\"mobilePaddingLeft\":0,\"mobileBlockWidthUnit\":\"%\",\"showBlockBackground\":true,\"blockInnerWidth\":\"full\",\"align\":\"full\",\"noPaddings\":false,\"blockBackgroundBackgroundColorOpacity\":1} -->\n<div class=\"alignfull wp-block-ugb-container ugb-container ugb-6011e3b ugb-container--v2 ugb-container--design-basic ugb-main-block ugb-main-block--inner-full ugb--has-block-background\" id=\"\"><style>.ugb-6011e3b-wrapper.ugb-container__wrapper{border-radius:0px !important;background-color:rgba(255,255,255,1) !important}.ugb-6011e3b-wrapper > .ugb-container__side{align-items:center !important}.ugb-6011e3b-content-wrapper.ugb-container__content-wrapper{width:65% !important}.ugb-6011e3b.ugb-container{background-color:rgba(255,255,255,1)}@media screen and (max-width:768px){.ugb-6011e3b-content-wrapper.ugb-container__content-wrapper{width:100% !important}.ugb-6011e3b.ugb-container{margin-top:0px !important;margin-bottom:0px !important;padding-top:0px !important;padding-right:0px !important;padding-bottom:0px !important;padding-left:0px !important}}</style><div class=\"ugb-inner-block\"><div class=\"ugb-block-content\"><div class=\"ugb-container__wrapper ugb-6011e3b-wrapper ugb--shadow-0\"><div class=\"ugb-container__side\"><div class=\"ugb-container__content-wrapper ugb-6011e3b-content-wrapper\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Features</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Company valuation tool helps you to understand the value and potential of selected business. This is useful in multiple occasions, for example in ownership changes, partnerships and funding opportunity considerations. If you would like to learn more about company valuation, please visit <a href=\"https://company-valuation.com/what-is-valuation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">what is valuation</a> page.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In addition to the Valuation Report, we also provide an online platform which is an easy-to-use interface to view and modify the financial data of companies. It is also possible to modify these forecasts manually to see how different scenarios would impact the company valuation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We offer a freemium model for the sale of our reports. You will get access to the online platform and select three companies each month after you sign up for the system. From the selected companies you get both credit risk and valuation reports. After this, you can easily upgrade your subscription to obtain more reports every month or alternatively buy individual reports. You can read more about our pricing from&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.creditreports.dk/pricing/\">the pricing page</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At the moment, CreditReports.dk is in beta phase, during which we will offer full access to the system free of charge. Register now and start making better business decisions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:ugb/icon-list {\"iconShape\":\"circle\",\"iconColor\":\"#0693e3\",\"iconSize\":32,\"columns\":1,\"mobileColumns\":1,\"uniqueClass\":\"ugb-6a4b470\",\"marginTop\":40,\"paddingTop\":25,\"paddingBottom\":25,\"mobileBlockWidth\":100,\"mobileBlockWidthUnit\":\"%\",\"showBlockBackground\":true,\"blockInnerWidth\":\"full\",\"align\":\"full\",\"blockBackgroundBackgroundColor\":\"#eeeeee\",\"showBlockTitle\":true,\"blockTitleBottomMargin\":25,\"blockTitleFontWeight\":\"bold\",\"blockTitleTag\":\"h3\",\"contentAlign\":\"left\"} -->\n<div class=\"alignfull wp-block-ugb-icon-list ugb-icon-list ugb-6a4b470 ugb-icon-list--v2 ugb-icon--icon-check ugb-main-block ugb-main-block--inner-full ugb--has-block-background\" id=\"\"><style>.ugb-6a4b470 li{--icon-size:32px;margin-bottom:16px !important}.ugb-6a4b470 li::before{height:32px !important;width:32px !important;background-image:url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,')}.ugb-6a4b470 li ul{margin-bottom:16px !important}.ugb-6a4b470.ugb-icon-list ul{columns:1}.ugb-6a4b470 .ugb-inner-block{text-align:left}.ugb-6a4b470.ugb-icon-list{margin-top:40px !important;padding-top:25px !important;padding-bottom:25px !important;background-color:#eeeeee}.ugb-6a4b470.ugb-icon-list:before{background-color:#eeeeee}.ugb-6a4b470 .ugb-block-title{font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:25px}@media screen and (max-width:768px){.ugb-6a4b470.ugb-icon-list ul{columns:1 !important}.ugb-6a4b470.ugb-icon-list > .ugb-inner-block{width:100% !important}}</style><div class=\"ugb-inner-block\"><h3 class=\"ugb-block-title\">What information does the report offer?</h3><div class=\"ugb-block-content\"><ul><li>Automatically generated estimates and company valuation reports</li><li>Easy-to-use tools for analyzing and modifying your own scenarios</li><li>Wide range of valuation methods</li><li>Comparisons and data with over 300,000 Danish companies from Danish Central Business Register</li></ul></div></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:ugb/icon-list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column {\"width\":50} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":1716,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"/assets/wordpress-media/2020/08/valureport-summary.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1716\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":50} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":1717,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"/assets/wordpress-media/2020/07/new_report_page2-min-724x1024.png\"><img src=\"/assets/wordpress-media/2020/08/valureport-dcf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1717\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To see what our valuation report looks like in detail, you can view the sample report by clicking the button below. You can also try the system yourself with a demo company and see how the system works. After you are convinced with your findings, please sign up to receive your free reports and to start using our service.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:ugb/button {\"design\":\"fullwidth\",\"showButton2\":true,\"showButton3\":true,\"button1FontSize\":20,\"button1Design\":\"basic\",\"button1Size\":\"medium\",\"button1TextColor\":\"#eeeeee\",\"button1BackgroundColor\":\"#0693e3\",\"button1PaddingTop\":9,\"button1PaddingRight\":28,\"button1PaddingBottom\":9,\"button1PaddingLeft\":28,\"button1BorderRadius\":10,\"button1Shadow\":0,\"button1NoFollow\":true,\"button2FontSize\":20,\"button2Size\":\"medium\",\"button2TextColor\":\"#eeeeee\",\"button2BackgroundColor\":\"#0693e3\",\"button2PaddingTop\":9,\"button2PaddingRight\":28,\"button2PaddingBottom\":9,\"button2PaddingLeft\":28,\"button2BorderRadius\":10,\"button2Shadow\":0,\"button2NoFollow\":true,\"button3FontSize\":20,\"button3Size\":\"medium\",\"button3PaddingTop\":9,\"button3PaddingRight\":28,\"button3PaddingBottom\":9,\"button3PaddingLeft\":28,\"button3BorderRadius\":10,\"button3NoFollow\":true,\"uniqueClass\":\"ugb-6a0c18b\",\"blockWidth\":600} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-ugb-button ugb-button-wrapper ugb-6a0c18b ugb-button--design-fullwidth ugb-main-block\" id=\"\"><style>.ugb-6a0c18b .ugb-button1 .ugb-button--inner{font-size:20px}.ugb-6a0c18b .ugb-button1{background-color:#0693e3;padding-top:9px;padding-right:28px;padding-bottom:9px;padding-left:28px;border-radius:10px !important}.ugb-6a0c18b .ugb-button1 .ugb-button--inner,.ugb-6a0c18b .ugb-button1 svg{color:#eeeeee !important}.ugb-6a0c18b .ugb-button1:before{border-radius:10px !important}.ugb-6a0c18b .ugb-button2 .ugb-button--inner{font-size:20px}.ugb-6a0c18b .ugb-button2{background-color:#0693e3;padding-top:9px;padding-right:28px;padding-bottom:9px;padding-left:28px;border-radius:10px !important}.ugb-6a0c18b .ugb-button2 .ugb-button--inner,.ugb-6a0c18b .ugb-button2 svg{color:#eeeeee !important}.ugb-6a0c18b .ugb-button2:before{border-radius:10px !important}.ugb-6a0c18b .ugb-button3 .ugb-button--inner{font-size:20px}.ugb-6a0c18b .ugb-button3{padding-top:9px;padding-right:28px;padding-bottom:9px;padding-left:28px;border-radius:10px !important}.ugb-6a0c18b .ugb-button3:before{border-radius:10px !important}.ugb-6a0c18b.ugb-button-wrapper > .ugb-inner-block{width:600px !important}</style><div class=\"ugb-inner-block\"><div class=\"ugb-block-content\"><div class=\"ugb-button-container\"><a class=\"ugb-button1 ugb-button ugb-button--size-medium\" href=\"https://creditanalysis.valuatum.com/AspAndUserCreation.action?templateAspQueryKey=CreditAnalysis\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span class=\"ugb-button--inner\">Sign up</span></a></div><div class=\"ugb-button-container\"><a class=\"ugb-button2 ugb-button ugb-button--size-medium\" href=\"/assets/wordpress-media/2020/08/valuation_report_demo.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span class=\"ugb-button--inner\">Sample report</span></a></div><div class=\"ugb-button-container\"><a class=\"ugb-button3 ugb-button ugb-button--size-medium\" href=\"https://platform.creditreports.dk/QuickLogin.action?key=3917&amp;x=qweasd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span class=\"ugb-button--inner\">Try the system</span></a></div></div></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:ugb/button -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Explore how this valuation tool works</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Video is provided by Valuatum, the software company behind this platform.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/RCqo-1ph-Gs\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></div>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:ugb/container -->",
  "markdown": "# COMPANY VALUATION TOOL\n\nCompany valuation tool provides you a reliable estimate for the value of a company. As in our credit reports, the valuation report can be generated by either using automatically generated estimates or user-modified scenarios.\n\n## **Features**\n\nCompany valuation tool helps you to understand the value and potential of selected business. This is useful in multiple occasions, for example in ownership changes, partnerships and funding opportunity considerations. If you would like to learn more about company valuation, please visit [what is valuation](https://company-valuation.com/what-is-valuation/) page.\n\nIn addition to the Valuation Report, we also provide an online platform which is an easy-to-use interface to view and modify the financial data of companies. It is also possible to modify these forecasts manually to see how different scenarios would impact the company valuation.\n\nWe offer a freemium model for the sale of our reports. You will get access to the online platform and select three companies each month after you sign up for the system. From the selected companies you get both credit risk and valuation reports. After this, you can easily upgrade your subscription to obtain more reports every month or alternatively buy individual reports. You can read more about our pricing from [the pricing page](https://www.creditreports.dk/pricing/).\n\nAt the moment, CreditReports.dk is in beta phase, during which we will offer full access to the system free of charge. Register now and start making better business decisions.\n\n### What information does the report offer?\n\n- Automatically generated estimates and company valuation reports\n- Easy-to-use tools for analyzing and modifying your own scenarios\n- Wide range of valuation methods\n- Comparisons and data with over 300,000 Danish companies from Danish Central Business Register\n\n![](/assets/wordpress-media/2020/08/valureport-summary.jpg)\n\n![](/assets/wordpress-media/2020/08/valureport-dcf.jpg)\n\nTo see what our valuation report looks like in detail, you can view the sample report by clicking the button below. You can also try the system yourself with a demo company and see how the system works. After you are convinced with your findings, please sign up to receive your free reports and to start using our service.\n\nSign up\n\nSample report\n\nTry the system\n\n## **Explore how this valuation tool works**\n\nVideo is provided by Valuatum, the software company behind this platform."
}
